children.fi_GhTextContent_text:
Next, import your project into GreenHouse Architect!

Organize your data exchange in the project and perform a one-click export.

GreenHouse Architect Benefits:
- Import fonts, colors, themes, images, etc.
- Easily structure and bind data
- Ability to add custom QML components

You can also generate a simulator and unit tests.
children.name: fi_GHBody

children.fi_GhTextContent_text:
Test and run your final Application!


- Platform agnostic Qt/QML code

- Enforces layered architecture

- Reusable, testable, simulatable code

- Pixel-perfect UI as specified in Figma

Learn More: https://www.ics.com/greenhouse
children.name: fi_GHBody

children.fi_GhTextContent_text:
Start your GreenHouse project with Figma!

Benefits:
- Designers get constant control over look and feel
- Reduces time to generate assets
- Easy handoff from UX designers
- Import Sketch, Photoshop, etc.

Alternatively, design directly in GreenHouse
